<th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Died</th>
<td class="infobox-data">28 May 1864<span style="display:none">(1864-05-28)</span> (aged 55)<br><div style="display:inline" class="deathplace">Fântâna Gorgana, <a href="/wiki/S%C3%A2nmihaiu_Alma%C8%99ului" title="Sânmihaiu Almașului">Sânmihaiu Almașului</a>, <a href="/wiki/Kolozs_County" title="Kolozs County">Kolozs County</a>,<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>2<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> Principality of Transylvania, Austrian Empire</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
